# Libraries

```{r}
library("dynlm")
library("stargazer")
```


# Data Upload

```{r}
finaldf <- read.csv("export2.csv")

str(finaldf)
```

```{r}
final.tsdf <- ts(finaldf, frequency = 12, start = c(1995, 10))
```

# Regression 

```{r}
lm1 <- dynlm(SeasCount.Report ~ prop.fem + prop.priv + FRBKCLMCIM + LREM25TTUSM156S, final.tsdf)
```

```{r}
stargazer(lm1, type = "text")
```
